      • estimateEntropy

        public double estimateEntropy(PasswordData passwordData)
        Calculates the entropy of the given PasswordData based on the specified password rules specified. It's important to note that this method does NOT take into account IllegalRegexRule or AllowedRegexRule as the regular expressions driving the rules may be negative matches.
        Parameters:
        passwordData - to estimate entropy for
        Returns:
        entropy estimate
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - for unknown PasswordData.Origin or if the required CharacterRule instances are unavailable in the passwordRules of this validator instance.
        See Also:
        PDF Publication
